OL,3,CTwo men charged with historic sex
OL,4,Coffences at Welsh children's centre
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged with
OL,7,Fhistoric child sexual exploitation at
OL,8,Fa former children's centre in Wales.
OL,10,FGwent Police said the two men have
OL,11,Fbeen charged with 45 alleged offences
OL,12,Fbetween them, relating to 16 victims.
OL,14,FThe alleged sexual and physical
OL,15,Foffences took place predominantly at
OL,16,Fthe Coed Glas Assessment Centre in
OL,17,FAbergavenny, between the 1970s and
OL,18,F1990s.
