OL,6,FAngus Riddell, 69, of Cwmbach, Rhondda
OL,7,FCynon Taf, has been charged with 38
OL,8,Foffences, including three counts of
OL,9,Findecent assault on a girl under the
OL,10,Fage of 16 and one count of attempted
OL,11,Findecent assault on a girl under the
OL,12,Fage of 16.
OL,14,FHe is also charged with 14 counts of
OL,15,Findecent assault on a boy under the
OL,16,Fage of 14 and 20 counts of assault,
OL,17,Fill-treatment, neglect, abandoning a
OL,18,Fchild, or causing a young person
OL,19,Funnecessary suffering or injury.
