OL,6,FRobin Griffiths, 65, from Ebbw Vale in
OL,7,FBlaenau Gwent, has been charged with
OL,8,Fseven counts of indecent assault on a
OL,9,Fboy under the age of 14.
OL,11,FBoth men were arrested on Friday June
OL,12,F20 and have been now been bailed to
OL,13,Fappear before Newport Magistrates'
OL,14,FCourt on July 3.
