OL,3,CTwo men charged with historic sex
OL,4,Coffences at Welsh children's centre
OL,6,FThe arrests come as part of Operation
OL,7,FSpinney, which has been investigating
OL,8,Freports made by men and women of
OL,9,Fsexual and physical abuse committed
OL,10,Fagainst them as children,
OL,11,Fpredominantly at the former assessment
OL,12,Fcentre.
OL,14,FThe centre was the responsibility of
OL,15,Fthe former Gwent County Council and
OL,16,Fhas been closed since 1995.
