OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent Andrew
OL,7,FTuck of Gwent Police said: "A team of
OL,8,Fdetectives has been working closely
OL,9,Fwith the Crown Prosecution Service and
OL,10,Flocal authorities as part of a long-
OL,11,Frunning investigation into allegations
OL,12,Fof non-recent sexual offences relating
OL,13,Fto the former children's home in
OL,14,FAbergavenny.
OL,16,F"This has resulted in us being able to
OL,17,Fcharge two men for a number of sexual
OL,18,Foffences against children.
