OL,6,F"We take all reports of child
OL,7,Fexploitation seriously and would urge
OL,8,Fanyone who has suffered abuse or has
OL,9,Fconcerns about someone who may be
OL,10,Fsuffering to come forward and speak to
OL,11,Fthe police.
OL,13,F"We will listen to you and investigate
OL,14,Fall offences and also ensure you have
OL,15,Faccess to any help or support you
OL,16,Fneed."
