OL,6,FHannah von Dadelszen, Chief Crown
OL,7,FProsecutor of the Crown Prosecution
OL,8,FService, said: "The Crown Prosecution
OL,9,FService has received a full file of
OL,10,Fevidence from the Gwent Police and has
OL,11,Fauthorised the investigation team to
OL,12,Fcharge two defendants with multiple
OL,13,Fcounts of child sexual offences.
OL,15,F"This charging decision was made by
OL,16,Fthe Organised Child Sexual Abuse Unit,
OL,17,Fwhich has a team of specialist
OL,18,Fprosecutors to lead on these complex
OL,19,Fand sensitive cases.
